# Example: $now

Color clock that circles all hues every minute.

```html
<div mv-app=colorClock  style="background: hsl([hue], 100%, 80%)">
	<span property="hue">[$now * 6 / 1000 mod 360]</span>
	<time>[time($now)]</time>
</div>
<style>
body {
	font: bold 100% Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;
	margin: 0;
}

div { 
	display: flex;
	flex-flow: column;
	height: 100vh;
	padding: 1em;
	box-sizing: border-box;
}

time {
	font-size: 500%;
	flex: 1;
}

span {
	opacity: .5;
}
</style>
```

